Cia de Apa Oltenia SA, a Romanian
water utility, awarded contracts totalling 59.9 million-lei ($18
million) for infrastructure works in the southern county of
Dolj.  A 31.9 million-lei contract went to  Polystart Impex SRL  for
water works in the town of  Poiana Mare  and a 28 million-lei
contract to Constructii Erbasu SA for a construction project in
